# Hierarchy
University organizational hierarchy:

Rector manages: VP_Academic, VP_Finance, VP_Student

VP_Academic manages: Dean_Engineering, Dean_Science, Dean_Business
VP_Finance manages: Budget_Office, Procurement
VP_Student manages: Student_Affairs, Career_Center, Counseling

Dean_Engineering manages: CS_Dept, EE_Dept, ME_Dept
Dean_Science manages: Physics_Dept, Math_Dept, Chemistry_Dept
Dean_Business manages: MBA_Program, Finance_Dept

CS_Dept manages: Prof_AI, Prof_DB, Prof_SE

Visualize this university organizational hierarchy as a tree.

